{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"content":[{"text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This checkbox indicator has two available states:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to use a tri-state checkbox instead, refer to ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","text":"Cases forbidden by design","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or a read only situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have a selected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = true","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"anchor":"Suggestions","type":"heading","text":"Suggestions","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"According to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","text":"Design documentation","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","type":"reference","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"unified-design-system.orange.com","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering","level":2},{"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Orange-Compact","text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Version","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","type"